text: Cyclone Ashoba formed in the Bay of Bengal near Andaman, away from Visakhapatnam. Early forecasts called for cyclone Ashoba to affect the Tamil Nadu coast.it was expected to reach Oman coast on 11.06.2014 ==Other websites== *http://tamil.oneindia.com/news/india/new-cyclone-ashoba-near- andaman-214190.html *http://blog.keaweather.in/tag/cyclone-ashoba/ Category:2014 in weather Category:2014 in Asia Category:Tropical cyclones in Asia
